text: Attila Strochmayer (born 7 February 1962) is a Hungarian rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Hungary Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Budapest
